extendedInfo.description: This is an app that shows the song list for each Guitar Hero game.View songlists for each gameSearch for songs & artistsSort Songs ListsGet Video/Lyric ResultsSave songs to a list, add scoresDLC - 07/09/2010Please Rate and post suggestions!
